<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ض ي م<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٣١٦١ - ض ي م]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ضامَ يَضِيم، ضِمْ، ضَيْمًا، فهو ضائم، والمفعول مَضِيم<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• ضام جارَه:</span> قهره، ظلمه وأضرَّ به.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• ضام عدوَّه:</span> أذلَّه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">• ضامه حقَّه:</span> انتقصه وغبنه <span class="c1">"ضام الاستعمارُ حقَّ الشعوب في الحرِّيَّة"</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>